name: Gen 2 Virgin FancyBird!
bio: Good morning! My name's Gen 2 Virgin FancyBird!. I once peed on John F. Kennedy Jr.'s cat. They had it coming. Sometimes I daydream of a life full of eating until I loathe myself, hamburgers, and prank-calling celebrities. I can't wait to wake you up at 4am for seemingly no reason.
